        <item>
            <title>【有片睇】2023 Excel 世界電競賽，澳洲數據分析專家倪安德蟬聯</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/18/2023-excel-gaminig/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=2023-excel-gaminig</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/18/2023-excel-gaminig/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 11:53:02 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Excel]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[電競]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1211021</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>相信很多朋友上班時都會用到 Excel，但你知道這款生產力軟件也可以拿來「電競」嗎？2023 年 Excel 世界錦標賽由來自澳洲的數據分析專家倪安德再度蟬聯奪冠，贏得 3000 美元（約港幣 23,394.52 元）獎金。</p><p>今年 Excel 世界錦標賽（Microsoft Excel World Championship）剛剛在美國賭城拉斯維加斯圓滿結束，這項比賽同一時間跨平於 Twitch、YouTube 及 ESPN 直播。今年冠軍頭銜及 3,000 美元獎金繼續由去年冠軍倪安德蟬聯奪得。倪安德是來自澳洲的數據分析專家。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1211042" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-0-2-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-0-2-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-0-2-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-0-2-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-0-2-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-0-2-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1211041" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Las-128-Last-64-Rounds-1-19-15-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Las-128-Last-64-Rounds-1-19-15-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Las-128-Last-64-Rounds-1-19-15-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Las-128-Last-64-Rounds-1-19-15-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Las-128-Last-64-Rounds-1-19-15-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Las-128-Last-64-Rounds-1-19-15-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Excel 世界錦標賽每年都會假設一個案例，參賽者需要扭盡六壬使用 Excel 內的功能去解決這個「案例」，例如今年決賽的案例就有關穿梭機製作及行省採礦。比賽分為 3 部分，每部分 30 分鐘。比賽是以用 Excel 技巧為中心，但仍然有不同的聲光表演元素，讓觀眾看得熱血沸騰。今年比賽現場有 Excel 培訓師 Jon Acampora 和 Oz du Soleil 作旁白講解比賽。</p><p>今年比賽加入了新賽程，就是準決賽開始 7.5 分鐘後將會淘汰得分最低的參賽者，而系統出現故障令裁判團誤淘汰倪安德。過後裁判團開會商討後將錯誤歸咎於電腦故障，並重新邀請倪安德重新回歸比賽。倪安德在比賽尾聲完成了加分題，領先跟隨其後的選手達 196 分，而倪安德本人更在比賽餘下半分鐘時除低耳機，直接兩手一攤坐等勝利。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1211043" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-2-56-8-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-2-56-8-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-2-56-8-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-2-56-8-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-2-56-8-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-2-56-8-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>實際上 Excel 世界錦標賽已存在逾 10 年，不過去年 ESPN 才開始傳播這項才賽事。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_84596"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/UDGdPE_C9u8?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/3/23817220/excel-esports-espn-the-ocho-championship-start-time-watch">The Verge</a>、<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UDGdPE_C9u8">YouTube</a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://hk.news.yahoo.com/excel%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7-%E7%AB%9F%E9%82%84%E6%9C%89-%E5%A0%B4-%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%B6%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD-excel%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E9%8C%A6%E6%A8%99%E8%B3%BD%E5%9C%A8%E6%AF%94%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC-042841666.html">數位時代</a>、<a href="https://www.wsj.com/tech/microsoft-world-excel-championships-las-vegas-448c5f0b">Wall Street Journal</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/18/2023-excel-gaminig/game-channel/">【有片睇】2023 Excel 世界電競賽，澳洲數據分析專家倪安德蟬聯</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
